ugh, though I have not been able to write to thee oftener__. I hope thee art not been too troubled by the world's cruel hand, and I hope thee art well and in health. \n\nI have been keeping the lighthouse these many years, and I have been watching the sea with a keen eye, and I have been watching the stars and the moon__ \n\nI have not been able to write to thee oftener__ though I have not been able to see thee with such a keen eye__ though I have"}, {"v": 4, "s": 1, "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</think>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</think>\n\n\n\n\n\n</think>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</think>\n\n\n\n\n</think>\n\n"}, {"v": 5, "s": 1, "text": "Okay,Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!Okay!"}, {"v": 6, "s": 1, "text": "\n\n>\n\n>\n\n\n\n\n\n>\n\n\n\n\n\n>\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n><\n</think>\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n><\n><<><\n\n><\n\n><\n>\n\n><\n\n><;><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n><\n><\n><\n><\n><\n\n><\n\n><\n><\n\n